Subject:Have a problem!
I do not know what to start with that’s why I will start with the description of my character. I consider myself quite a knowledgeable and clever lady, also I am  very pretty and romantic. 
I adore kids, and I feel that it is time to have my own children.. It seems to be foolish to describe the man whom I want to see by my side. I am looking for normal, realistic man. For me it is very important to meet my other half. Though, I can say for sure that appearance is far from being very important. 
The inner beauty is much more important than beauty of the body. I want my man to be positive, communicative and very attentive. 

